    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, it's been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been super reliable for me. If you\u2019re looking for a dependable car that still looks great on the road, this is the one! I've taken great care of it, and I'd love to see it go to a nice new home. Feel free to reach out with any questions\u2014I'm happy to chat!",
      "price": 33500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
