      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 6
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Up for sale is a mechanically sound E46 M3, featuring the high-revving S54B32 inline-six engine equipped with individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing. This example retains its visceral performance characteristics, delivering power through a crisp 6-speed Getrag manual gearbox to the rear wheels via a factory M-Variable differential lock. The chassis has been maintained with an emphasis on handling precision, including reinforced subframe mounts and refreshed bushings to mitigate the common floor pan fatigue found in this generation. While the exterior shows the honest patina of a driver\u2019s car, the drivetrain remains robust, offering the linear power delivery and 8,000 RPM redline that defines the M-division's naturally aspirated era. Ideal for the enthusiast seeking a visceral, analog driving experience without the premium of a garage queen.",
